得聘用，申請回港工作。 <br />\n<br />\n保安局文件顯示，過去三年因為參與以上計劃獲得香港居留權的人數逐年上升，2016年有1979人、2017年有2172人，增加至去年有2455人，保安局未有提供當中多少是內地人。 <br />\n<br />\n而去年有關計劃的申請人數就有10200多宗，當中逾九成八獲批，超過九成是內地人。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，過去三年有超過11000名內地學生以留港就學為理由，申請延期逗留。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該你叫呢班傻仔快D 死返上深圳"},{"pid":"26a88c0c256cee66f2c9c54bf2d9917f11e3c153","tid":1043609,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7beabfbaf5067f17ac27e143625c515bba045a","tid":1043609,"uid":16985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:43:42.000Z","msg":"香港人有d 骨氣停用引入蝗既agent已經可以減少vd多蝗蟲入假<br />\n現實係無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faac6ecea6fdde5d51874902c7330b8c9ab38d51","tid":1043609,"uid":44038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T19:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614c13b9e6382e43848d4c87c992bb9e915124b5","tid":1043609,"uid":165510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T19:26:03.000Z","msg":"痴撚線每日150已經未計啲蝻 <br />\n又要再整多堆人落黎 香港就黎陸沉啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ef870b7340ec3202940353c1db586bc622d0ea","tid":1043609,"uid":86277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T22:02:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201805/08/P2018050800509.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201805%2F08%2FP2018050800509.htm&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWr%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=5ec8f0f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201805/08/P2018050800509.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2018-05-08 old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557c33d092caff267f01b081917bde94b778fc59","tid":1043609,"uid":42283,"like":2,